123
00:09:09,400 --> 00:09:11,000
Friend?

124
00:09:14,180 --> 00:09:17,730
Hui'er gave the Xuanbing Stone to Xiao Yuan to master the Fengming Saber

125
00:09:17,730 --> 00:09:21,160
