133
00:09:49,970 --> 00:09:53,050
- You are still my beloved Hui'er.
- What? Chief Xiao?

134
00:09:53,050 --> 00:09:57,410
- How could he be involved with a Qianyue Sect enchantress?
- Yes... yes...

135
00:09:57,410 --> 00:09:59,590
Qianyue Sect?

136
00:10:00,120 --> 00:10:03,110
Do you still say you have no relationship with Chief Xiao?

137
00:10:04,200 --> 00:10:06,120
