157
00:11:17,080 --> 00:11:21,620
Do you know that every year, on the 15th day of the eighth month,

158
00:11:21,620 --> 00:11:26,520
your father, who so deeply cared about the martial arts circle, hurried far away

159
00:11:26,520 --> 00:11:31,220
