166
00:12:03,530 --> 00:12:07,800
Regarding events of those years, no need to evade, Chief Li.

167
00:12:07,800 --> 00:12:09,660
You might as well tell everyone.

168
00:12:09,660 --> 00:12:13,240
I believe my father can withstand any test regarding his post.

169
00:12:15,420 --> 00:12:18,800
Twenty-four years ago, Xiao Yuan and I

170
00:12:18,800 --> 00:12:21,650
were hunted and poisoned by Xing servants.

171
00:12:21,650 --> 00:12:24,610
We accidentally entered the ice gorge of the nearby Qianyue Cave.

172
00:12:24,610 --> 00:12:26,880
Hui'er saved us.

173
00:12:43,720 --> 00:12:46,080
